            "questionText": "An isolated community is setting up a new solar farm. The solar farm produces an average of $!$250000$!$ $!$kWh$!$ of electrical energy daily. If it operates for $!$10$!$ hours each day, calculate the average electrical power generated by the farm in $!$kW$!$.",
