        {
            "id": "80dbffda90a94cf99d7a5",
            "questionText": "A team is designing a new portable power bank that provides a voltage gain of $!$5\\,V$!$ to charge a smartphone. If $!$1800\\,C$!$ of charge are transferred from the power bank to the phone, calculate the total change in electrical potential energy (in Joules).",
